msgstr "有关此类及其支持的方法的更多信息，请参阅 link:https://javadoc.io/doc/io.quarkus.resteasy.reactive/resteasy-reactive-client/latest/org/jboss/resteasy/reactive/client/api/ClientMultipartForm.html[ClientMultipartForm] 的 Javadoc。"

