#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Known limitations"
msgstr "已知限制"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"While the REST Client extension aims to be a drop-in replacement for the RESTEasy Client extension, there are some differences\n"
"and limitations:"
msgstr "虽然 REST 客户端扩展旨在作为 RESTEasy 客户端扩展的直接替代方案，但两者仍存在一些差异和限制："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"the default scope of the client for the new extension is `@ApplicationScoped` while the `quarkus-resteasy-client` defaults to `@Dependent`\n"
"To change this behavior, set the `quarkus.rest-client.scope` property to the fully qualified scope name."
msgstr "新扩展的客户端默认作用域为 `@ApplicationScoped，` 而 `quarkus-resteasy-client` 的默认作用域为 `@Dependent` 。若要更改此行为，请将 `quarkus.rest-client.scope` 属性设置为完全限定的作用域名称。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "it is not possible to set `SSLContext`"
msgstr "无法设置 `SSLContext`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "a few things that don't make sense for a non-blocking implementations, such as setting the `ExecutorService`, don't work"
msgstr "对于非阻塞实现来说，有些操作（例如设置 `ExecutorService` ）并不合理，因此无法正常工作"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Import things to be aware of"
msgstr "导入时需注意的事项"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Concurrent requests"
msgstr "并发请求"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The REST Client uses the Vert.x HTTP connection pool with a default size of `50`  in order to minimize the necessary HTTP connections being used against the target REST services.\n"
"While this is a reasonable default, it might be too limiting for specific scenarios. In such cases, the `quarkus.rest-client.\"some-client\".connection-pool-size` configuration property can be used."
msgstr "REST 客户端使用 Vert.x HTTP 连接池，其默认大小为 `50` ，以尽量减少与目标 REST 服务建立的必要 HTTP 连接数量。虽然这是一个合理的默认值，但在某些特定场景下可能过于限制。 在这种情况下，可以使用 `quarkus.rest-client.\"some-client\".connection-pool-size` 配置属性。"

